  <brief_title>Adalimumab in Rheumatoid Arthritis. An Investigation of Wholebody MRI, Conventional MRI, CT and Circulating Biomarkers</brief_title>
  <official_title>Adalimumab in Rheumatoid Arthritis. An Investigation of Changes in Disease Activity and Course of Joint Destruction by Use of 3 Tesla Whole-Body MRI, Dedicated 3 Tesla MRI and CT of the Hand, and Soluble Biomarkers</official_title>
