  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Adalimumab in rheumatoid arthritis. An investigation of changes in disease activity and
      course of joint destruction by use of 3 Tesla Whole-Body MRI, dedicated 3 Tesla MRI and CT of
      the hand, and soluble biomarkers. Furthermore to compare ultrasound examination with
      wholebody MRI etc.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
